Dark Mode session.

00:00:33.526 --> 00:00:34.616 A:middle
My name is Raymond Sepulveda,

00:00:35.106 --> 00:00:36.866 A:middle
and I'm a macOS designer on the

00:00:36.866 --> 00:00:38.136 A:middle
Human Interface Design team.

