The more important text is given

00:31:50.396 --> 00:31:51.856 A:middle
the labelColor, and the less

00:31:51.856 --> 00:31:53.436 A:middle
important text is

00:31:53.436 --> 00:31:54.496 A:middle
secondaryLabelColor.

00:31:55.196 --> 00:31:59.006 A:middle
To find out which colors are

00:31:59.006 --> 00:32:01.296 A:middle
dynamic, in the Interface


00:31:59.006 --> 00:32:01.296 A:middle
dynamic, in the Interface

00:32:01.396 --> 00:32:03.886 A:middle
Builder popup menu for colors,

00:32:04.106 --> 00:32:05.626 A:middle
it'll show you the list, and

00:32:05.626 --> 00:32:07.056 A:middle
they've done a really nice job

00:32:07.056 --> 00:32:09.726 A:middle
of making those be the dynamic

00:32:09.776 --> 00:32:10.146 A:middle
colors.

00:32:11.716 --> 00:32:14.876 A:middle
So, now switching, once we know

00:32:14.876 --> 00:32:17.016 A:middle
that, black color and dark gray

00:32:17.586 --> 00:32:19.686 A:middle
to labelColor and

00:32:19.686 --> 00:32:21.756 A:middle
secondaryLabelColor, this fixes

00:32:21.756 --> 00:32:23.866 A:middle
our text, and it looks great in

00:32:23.866 --> 00:32:25.586 A:middle
